text: LA-39 is a constituency of Azad Kashmir Legislative Assembly which is currently represented by Asad Aleem Shah of Pakistan Muslim League (N). It covers the area of Rawalpindi City in Pakistan. Only refugees from Kashmir Valley settled in Pakistan are eligible to vote. ==Election 2016== elections were held in this constituency on 21 July 2016.
